        <p>THE TRUE ISSUE OR "THATS WHATS THE MATTER".<note type="editorial" n="1"/>"That's What's
          the Matter" is a pro-Union Civil War song by American folk musician Stephen Foster. The
          chorus proclaims "That's what's the matter / The rebels have to scatter." Music and lyrics
          can be accessed at <ref target="http://www.civilwarpoetry.org/union/songs/matter.html"
            >www.civilwarpoetry.org/union/songs/matter.html</ref>.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="image_transcription" n="2" facs="#imprint">
        <head>
          <supplied resp="editorial">Imprint</supplied>
        </head>
