            <orgName key="ENT.000000844">Currier &amp; Ives</orgName>, in the Clerk's Office of the
          District Court of the United States, for the Southern Dist. of N.Y.</p>
        <p>Published by Currier &amp; Ives, 152 Nassau St. N.Y.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="image_transcription" n="3" facs="#lincoln">
        <head>
          <persName key="ENT.000000447">Lincoln.</persName>
        </head>
        <p>No peace without Abolition!</p>
      </div>
      <div type="image_transcription" n="4" facs="#mac">
        <head>
          <persName key="ENT.000001783">Mac.</persName>
        </head>
